data.title: Richtech Robotics (RR) Is Up 22.0% After U.S. Robotics Push And New AI Partnership News
data.description: In recent days, reports that the Trump administration is preparing an executive order and broader initiatives to accelerate U.S. robotics development have put Richtech Robotics in the spotlight, alongside news of Commerce Secretary Howard Lutnick meeting with industry CEOs. Richtech Robotics also announced a collaboration with NomadGo to integrate AI into inventory management, highlighting how policy momentum and product innovation are converging around the company’s automation...
data.keywords: Howard Lutnick, Richtech Robotics, executive order, Robotics research
